The Independent National Electoral Commission has begun the collation of results for the presidential and National Assembly elections in Rivers State. Of the results so far collated, the presidential candidate of the All Progressives Congress, Bola Tinubu, won in two of the three local government areas so far released. The local governments are Ahoada West, Tai and Opobo/Nkoro. The APC won in Tai and Opobo/Nkoro, while the Labour Party won in Ahoada West. The distribution of the results so far release are as follows: Ahoada West: APC – 3443
LP – 4634
PDP – 2582 Tai LGA APC: 9442
LP 485
PDP 1506 Opobo/Nkoro APC: 5701
LP: 2093
PDP: 1542